Former governor of the State and Senator representing Imo West  Senatorial District, Owelle Rochas Okorocha has congratulated Sen. Hope  Uzodinma over his Victory at the Supreme Court which declared him the  new governor of the State. Okorocha, according to a statement by his media aide, Sam Onwuemeodo, also Congratulated the APC members in Imo for the Victory. He called on all hands to be on deck for the support of the new
governor. Owelle Okorocha assured Senator Uzodinma of his unflinching
Support. 